ğŸ”‘ One-Liner Summary

NAT â†’ Internet milega, but VM sirf apna kaam karega (safe & easy).

Bridge â†’ VM ko host jaisa hi network identity milta hai (LAN me dikhai deta hai).

Host-Only â†’ VM aur host ek dusre se baat kar sakte hain, internet nahi.

